article.headline: Pascarelli scores 26 as Marist beats Dartmouth 63-53
article.description: — Josh Pascarelli's 26 points helped Marist defeat Dartmouth 63-53 on Saturday night.
article.linkText: Pascarelli scores 26 as Marist beats Dartmouth 63-53
article.story: HANOVER, N.H. -- — Josh Pascarelli's 26 points helped Marist defeat Dartmouth 63-53 on Saturday night. Pascarelli had seven rebounds for the Red Foxes (6-2). Max Allen scored 12 points and added five rebounds. Kam Farris had nine points and shot 3 for 10, including 3 for 8 from beyond the arc. The Big Green (2-6) were led in scoring by Ryan Cornish, who finished with 14 points. Dartmouth also got 13 points from Jayden Williams. Jackson Munro also had nine points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
